account.descriptionLink: This proposal is to mint 8,000,000,000 $SOCK tokens, symbolizing 1 token for every person on Earth. These tokens will serve as the governance and utility tokens for the World Sock Exchange DAO. The initial supply will be allocated to the DAO treasury, with future proposals deciding on token distribution strategies, such as rewards for community participation, trading incentives, and governance initiatives
account.name: Proposal to Mint $SOCK Tokens: 1 for Every Person on Earth
